uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl

Class OMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.owl.OMonitor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OLogger

    public abstract class OMonitor
extends java.lang.Object
    Monitor for loading of the OWL ontology and loading of the reasoner.

    The class maintains a static list of current monitors, whose appropriate methods will be invoked at the relevant points in the build process.
